{
    "issue": 162,
    "engine": "dw-cohesion",
    "gameSystem": "dw",
    "datamodel": {
        "mixinFile": "src/module/data/actor/mixins/dw-cohesion-template.ts",
        "applyTo": "CharacterData",
        "schemaFieldsExport": "dwCohesionSchemaFields",
        "declarationsTypeExport": "DwCohesionDeclarations"
    },
    "sheetPanel": {
        "partialPath": "systems/wh40k-rpg/templates/actor/panel/dw-cohesion-panel.hbs",
        "preloadEntry": "systems/wh40k-rpg/templates/actor/panel/dw-cohesion-panel.hbs",
        "includeIn": "src/templates/actor/player/tab-status.hbs",
        "gateOn": "isDW",
        "contextKey": "cohesionPanel",
        "contextBuilder": {
            "description": "Compute cohesionPanel from actor.system.{cohesionCurrent,cohesionMax,cohesionLostThisTurn,rallied}.",
            "shape": {
                "current": "actor.system.cohesionCurrent",
                "max": "actor.system.cohesionMax",
                "lostThisTurn": "actor.system.cohesionLostThisTurn",
                "rallied": "actor.system.rallied",
                "canRally": "!actor.system.rallied",
                "canRecover": "actor.system.cohesionCurrent < actor.system.cohesionMax && actor.system.cohesionMax > 0"
            },
            "gate": "this._resolveGameSystemId() === 'dw'"
        }
    },
    "actions": [
        { "actionName": "dwCohesionRally", "module": "src/module/actions/dw-cohesion-actions.ts", "exportName": "dwCohesionRally" },
        { "actionName": "dwCohesionRecoverObjective", "module": "src/module/actions/dw-cohesion-actions.ts", "exportName": "dwCohesionRecoverObjective" },
        { "actionName": "dwCohesionChallenge", "module": "src/module/actions/dw-cohesion-actions.ts", "exportName": "dwCohesionChallenge" }
    ],
    "chatPartial": {
        "partialPath": "systems/wh40k-rpg/templates/chat/dw-cohesion-chat.hbs",
        "preloadEntry": "systems/wh40k-rpg/templates/chat/dw-cohesion-chat.hbs"
    },
    "i18nKeys": "WH40K.DW.Cohesion.*",
    "e2eSpec": "tests/e2e/dw-cohesion.spec.ts",
    "storybookStories": [
        "src/templates/actor/panel/dw-cohesion-panel.stories.ts",
        "src/templates/chat/dw-cohesion-chat.stories.ts"
    ],
    "notes": [
        "isDW context flag does not yet exist in character-sheet.ts; orchestrator must add `const isDW = activeGameSystem === 'dw'; context.isDW = isDW;` alongside the existing isBC/isDH2 lines and gate the panel context build on it.",
        "All four schema fields default to 0/false; non-DW actors that happen to be reflected over this schema stay invisible via the isDW panel gate. A future dedicated kill-team actor type can spread the same dwCohesionSchemaFields() into its defineSchema().",
        "The CohesionMax derivation (leader Fellowship Bonus + Rank/Command table) is intentionally left to the orchestrator's prepareDerivedData() wiring — the resolver maxCohesion() in rules/dw-cohesion.ts is the function to call once the leader-detection logic lands.",
        "The action handlers' DwCohesionActionHost interface is a structural duck-type matching CharacterSheet's relevant surface (actor + _notify). No applications/* coupling from the actions module."
    ]
}
